University Website Design
A responsive and modern University Website UI built using HTML, CSS
This project demonstrates a complete front-end design for an educational institution website with multiple sections and a mobile-friendly navigation menu.

🚀 Features
🏫 Hero section with background image and overlay
📚 Courses section (Intermediate, Degree, Post Graduation)
🌍 Global campus showcase with hover effects
🏀 Facilities section (Library, Playground, Cafeteria)
💬 Student testimonials section
📞 Call-to-action (CTA) section
📱 Responsive navigation menu (open/close toggle)
🎨 Smooth hover and transition effects
🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3 (Flexbox & Media Queries)
JavaScript (DOM Manipulation)
Font Awesome (Icons)
Google Fonts (Poppins)
